{
  "stem": "2350.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So there was a powder room that they had the-- the explosive, that they put into the grenade.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So from that, they were taking out the powder and giving it to the men somehow.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "This was all-- probably that nobody knew, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It wasn't spread out through the-- through the barracks or through the people, that everybody should know what's going on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That's why I didn't know, and I wasn't interested to know what's going on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So that's what happened to-- to those four girls.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then came January 18th, the dead march.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went to work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And somebody came over to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know the way to go home?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That the Russians are already in Zawiercie.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I says, how would I know a way to run back home?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I says, I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That the civilian master told her that the Russians are already in our home town.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we probably-- that all Birkenau is evacuated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we're going to be evacuated from Auschwitz tonight.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we came back to the blocks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was no food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were thousands of-- tens of thousands of people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we marched out at night in cold and snow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The jets were-- the-- the bombers were-- were flying.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know who they are-- English, American, or Russian.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we walked at night, the whole night, until we came to a village.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We slept with pigs just to warm up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we walked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was two or three days.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't know where we going in cold.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the snow was coming in-- till we came to Gleiwitz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in Gleiwitz, this was the dead march.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in Gleiwitz, we went into the open cattle cars with snow, with ice on the bottom.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
